WEBVTT

00:08:27.701 --> 00:08:31.725
I had, at this point,
seen some unfathomable things,

00:08:31.749 --> 00:08:34.579
but this, by far,
was the most heart-stopping.

00:08:35.055 --> 00:08:37.301
You see, Eric is a really big guy,

00:08:37.325 --> 00:08:41.653
and it took two aides
and a lifting machine

00:08:41.677 --> 00:08:43.034
to get him dressed.

00:08:43.498 --> 00:08:47.190
I sat and watched this process
for over two hours.

00:08:47.214 --> 00:08:50.193
When I expressed my shock to Eric,

00:08:50.217 --> 00:08:51.450
he looked at me and said,

00:08:51.474 --> 00:08:53.906
"Mindy, this is every single day.

00:08:54.433 --> 00:08:55.748
What can I say?

00:08:55.772 --> 00:08:57.155
I like to look sharp."

00:08:58.290 --> 00:08:59.739
Research done.